.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, ebony, turquise, light-blood-red, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, chinese, polish, mexican
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, dunhill, alhambra, blend, vegafina
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, juice, mirinda, iced-tea
5 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, goldfish, ferret, cat

1. the colombian is the person who likes black
2. the dutch is the owner of the pony
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes ebony
4. the chinese is the person drinking lemonade
5. the person who likes ebony is to the right of the person who likes turquise
6. the swisher-smoker is the owner of the cat
7. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes light-blood-red
8. the person drinking juice is in the middle
9. the polish is on the far left
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard
11. the dunhill-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the ferret
12. the blend-smoker is the person drinking mirinda
13. the mexican is the vegafina-smoker
14. the polish is to the left or right of the person who likes blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   polish	|    chinese	|     colombian	|    dutch	|    mexican	|
| Color		|    light-blood-red	|      blood-red	|      black	|     turquise	|     ebony	|
| Beverage	|     iced-tea	|      lemonade	|      juice	| mirinda	|     7up	|
| Cigar		|     dunhill	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| blend	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     lizard	|     ferret	|     cat	|     pony	|     goldfish	|
